I had visited Dr Abhishek Chauhan for Hair transplant. Hair Transplant surgery was done at an unbelievably reasonable cost which I couldn't find anywhere else in Mumbai. 
Hospitality provided by Dr and his team was remarkable.Special attention was given by Dr to explain me the entire procedure and he is very soft spoken in nature. you can approach Dr Abhishek very easily and he will even reply your messages whenever he finds time from his schedule. Surgery was absolutely painless. Would recommend for hair transplant.

My son Aryadutt, milk tooth was broken due to accident while playing, Dr. Abhishek diagnosed it and explained me about the bone structure growth jaw growth till the age of 12, also assured that don't need to worry as of now, at the age of 12 we can take a call if any care or precaution is needed for the growth of tooth naturally with its alignment with other teeths. I am really satisfied n happy the way their team works.

I had consulted dr Abhishek for  an implant supported Denture case for my mother who is 70 years old. Doctor Abhishek and his team were very efficient and the entire ecosystem at Sharan hospital is very well designed to efficiently cater to patients. He was very patient with all our naive queries, was very knowledgeable and guided us with great care right from choosing the right denture to getting the implant in place. He would stretch beyond his consulting hours to personally tweak the denture and ensuring my mother tried it multiple times until she was completely satisfied with the fit. He showed great care and love as he dealt with this elderly patient. My mother was very happy with his behaviour and care . I would highly recommend consulting Dr Abhishek. *** ** *** **** ******** * **** *** ** ******************
